scenes.description: Yukihana Lamy performing her song 'Muteki Honki da Survivor' on stage with backup dancers.
Lamy poses after the song, breathing heavily as the audience cheers.
MC section where Lamy talks to the audience about the live and the new music video.
Preview of the animated music video for 'Muteki Honki da Survivor'.
Announcement of the MV premiere and scrolling end credits.
